---
import SectionTitle from "./UI/SectionTitle.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="section-padding">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <SectionTitle title="About Me" />

    <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="reveal-left">
        <div class="relative mx-auto w-fit">
          <div class="relative h-80 w-72 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border-2 border-surface-300 md:h-96 md:w-80">
            <img
              src="/photo.png"
              alt="Abhiram Rathod"
              class="h-full w-full object-cover"
              width="320"
              height="384"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 -z-10 h-full w-full rounded-2xl border-2 border-primary/30"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal-right space-y-6">
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
          Hey there! <span class="inline-block origin-bottom-right">&#128075;</span>
        </h3>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
          I'm <span class="text-white font-medium">Abhiram</span>, a passionate
          and adaptive Software Developer who enjoys solving real-world problems
          through clean, scalable, and efficient code. I'm driven by continuous
          learning and a deep curiosity for how technology can power innovation.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
          I graduated from <span class="text-primary-light font-medium">NIT Tiruchirappalli</span>,
          one of India's premier engineering institutes, and began my professional
          journey with <span class="text-primary-light font-medium">Amdocs</span>
          through campus placement. Since then, I've been contributing to the
          RealTime Billing Product, working on complex systems in a
          production-critical environment.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
          At Amdocs, I've developed solid experience with Java, Spring Boot, and
          Microservices Architecture, while expanding my skills across Kafka,
          Couchbase, Kubernetes, REST APIs, and more. I'm always seeking
          opportunities to build robust, distributed systems and continuously
          level up my engineering craft.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 pt-4">
          <div class="glass-card px-6 py-4 text-center">
            <span class="block font-display text-3xl font-bold text-primary">1+</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-400">Year at Amdocs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card px-6 py-4 text-center">
            <span class="block font-display text-3xl font-bold text-primary">NIT</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-400">Trichy '24</span>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card px-6 py-4 text-center">
            <span class="block font-display text-3xl font-bold text-primary">4</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-400">Certifications</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
